text.tspan: Life expectation age 45, by sex, United States
Life expectation at birth for those currently aged 45, by sex, for the United States. For example in 1790, a 45 year old
female could expect to live until the age of 69.
Source: OWID based on Hacker (2010) and the US Social Security Administration (2017)
